# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

## [0.1] - 2022-03-23
- Initial tagged release, includes several features:
  - EGIAuthenticator, simplifies the use of Check-in with JupyterHub
  - EGI Spawner, simplifies the use kubespawner with Check-in identities
  - onedata authenticator and spawner, that extend the EGI authenticator
    and spawner to interact with onedata (mount spaces)
  - D4Science authenticator and spawner for integration with the D4Science
    platform
  - Welcome page for showing an intro page to users
  - Custom templates for login and error pages
